'''ICARE Institute of Medical Sciences & Research''' is a private [[medical college]] located in [[Haldia]], [[West Bengal]]. It was established in 2011. The institute offers undergraduate seats for [[MBBS]] and postgraduate course MD (Pathology, Pharmacology, Microbiology, Biochemistry) which are recognised by the [[Medical Council of India]]. It is established by an society named Indian Centre for Advancent of Research and EDUCATION (ICARE). A 500 bedded multispeciality Bidhan Chanda Roy Hospital is attached with it.

